metadata.name: Itsuki #1
metadata.description: Itsuki is an NFT collection where art is the priority, giving back to nature and supporting women in tech, nft & games is the vision. Itsuki team is doxed and has been in the NFT space for more than 1 and half years as artists. They have been building Itsuki for more than 5 months and growing the community organically. On every mint, Itsuki will be planting a real tree in a real-world and start a new era in the crypto world. Where the way trees maintain the life balance in the environment. In the same way it will play a major role in carbon neutrality and yet create a utility for the holder with the power of GameFi. We are not just an NFT project, We are an Initiative. We are Itsuki
